    "chemicalDescription": [
      "rh-Polypeptide-11 Dipeptide-19 Oligopeptide-91 Hexapeptide-40 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from rh-Polypeptide-11, Dipeptide-19, Oligopeptide-91 and Hexapeptide-40. The fused peptide contains 184 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
